# Frontend UI Conventions (Next.js + Tailwind + shadcn/ui)

Tech stack: Next.js 16 (App Router, RSC), React 19, TypeScript (strict), Tailwind CSS v4, shadcn/ui (radix-lyra), Phosphor Icons.

---

## 1. Folder Structure

```
randomz-fe/
├── app/                    # App Router pages & layouts
│   ├── layout.tsx          # Root layout
│   ├── page.tsx            # Home page
│   ├── globals.css         # Global styles & Tailwind
│   └── {route}/
│       ├── page.tsx        # Route page
│       ├── layout.tsx      # Route layout (if needed)
│       ├── loading.tsx     # Suspense fallback
│       ├── error.tsx       # Error boundary
│       └── not-found.tsx   # 404 UI
├── components/
│   ├── ui/                 # shadcn/ui primitives (do NOT edit manually)
│   └── web/                # App-specific custom components
├── hooks/                  # Custom React hooks
├── lib/                    # Utilities (cn, api helpers, constants)
└── types/                  # Shared TypeScript types
```

---

## 2. Server vs Client Components

**Default: Server Component.** Chỉ thêm `"use client"` khi thực sự cần.

| Cần `"use client"`                      | Không cần                    |
| --------------------------------------- | ---------------------------- |
| `useState`, `useEffect`, hooks          | Hiển thị data từ props/fetch |
| Event handlers (`onClick`, `onChange`)  | Conditional rendering        |
| Browser APIs (`localStorage`, `window`) | Server data fetching         |
| Third-party client libs                 | Static UI, layouts           |

### Pattern: tách Server/Client

Khi một page cần cả server data lẫn interactivity, tách thành hai file:

```tsx
// app/room/page.tsx — Server Component (fetch data)
import { getRooms } from "@/lib/endpoints/room"
import { RoomList } from "@/components/web/room-list"

export default async function RoomPage() {
  const { data } = await getRooms()
  return <RoomList rooms={data.content} />
}
```

```tsx
// components/web/room-list.tsx — Client Component (interactivity)
"use client"

import type { RoomResponse } from "@/types/room"

export function RoomList({ rooms }: { rooms: RoomResponse[] }) {
  return (
    <ul>
      {rooms.map((room) => (
        <li key={room.id}>{room.name}</li>
      ))}
    </ul>
  )
}
```

> **Rule:** Đẩy `"use client"` xuống thấp nhất có thể trong component tree. Không đặt `"use client"` trên page.tsx chỉ vì một child cần interactivity.

