## 3. Component Conventions

### File Naming

- Files: **kebab-case** → `room-card.tsx`, `mode-toggle.tsx`
- Components: **PascalCase** → `RoomCard`, `ModeToggle`
- Hooks: **camelCase** với `use` prefix → `use-theme-shortcut.ts` (file), `useThemeShortcut` (export)

### Component Authoring

- Dùng **function declarations**, không dùng arrow functions cho components.
- Default export cho **pages và layouts**. Named export cho **reusable components**.

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD — reusable component
export function RoomCard({ room }: RoomCardProps) {
  return <div className="rounded border p-4">{room.name}</div>
}

// ✅ GOOD — page
export default function RoomPage() {
  return <main>Room</main>
}

// ❌ BAD — arrow function
const RoomCard = ({ room }: RoomCardProps) => { ... }
```

### Props

- Inline props cho component đơn giản (≤ 3 props).
- Extract `type` cho props phức tạp. Dùng `type`, không dùng `interface`.
- Nhận `className?: string` trên components có wrapper element.

```tsx
type RoomCardProps = {
  room: RoomResponse
  onJoin: (id: number) => void
  className?: string
}

export function RoomCard({ room, onJoin, className }: RoomCardProps) { ... }
```

---

## 4. Styling

- Luôn dùng Tailwind utility classes. Không CSS modules, không inline `style`.
- Dùng `cn()` từ `@/lib/utils` để merge conditional classes.
- Dùng shadcn/ui components từ `@/components/ui/` cho standard UI elements.
- Dùng `buttonVariants()` khi apply button styles lên non-button elements (e.g., `<Link>`).

```tsx
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils"

export function Card({ className, children }: { className?: string; children: React.ReactNode }) {
  return (
    <div className={cn("rounded border bg-card p-4 text-card-foreground", className)}>
      {children}
    </div>
  )
}
```

### Theme Colors

Dùng shadcn CSS variable tokens, không dùng raw Tailwind colors:

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD
<div className="bg-background text-foreground border-border" />
<div className="bg-muted text-muted-foreground" />
<div className="bg-primary text-primary-foreground" />

// ❌ BAD — raw colors phá dark mode
<div className="bg-white text-black border-gray-200" />
```

---

## 5. Navigation & Images

### Links — dùng `next/link`

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD
import Link from "next/link"
<Link href="/room/123">Vào phòng</Link>

// ❌ BAD — mất client-side navigation
<a href="/room/123">Vào phòng</a>
```

### Images — dùng `next/image`

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD
import Image from "next/image"
<Image src="/avatar.png" alt="Avatar người chơi" width={40} height={40} />

// ❌ BAD — mất optimization
<img src="/avatar.png" alt="Avatar" />
```

> `alt` luôn bắt buộc. Nếu ảnh là decorative, dùng `alt=""`.

