## 6. Pages, Layouts & Special Files

### Pages (`page.tsx`)

```tsx
export default function RoomPage() {
  return (
    <main>
      <h1 className="text-2xl font-bold">Rooms</h1>
    </main>
  )
}
```

### Layouts (`layout.tsx`)

```tsx
export default function RoomLayout({ children }: { children: React.ReactNode }) {
  return (
    <div className="flex gap-6">
      <aside className="w-64">Sidebar</aside>
      <main className="flex-1">{children}</main>
    </div>
  )
}
```

### Loading (`loading.tsx`)

Tự động wrap page trong `<Suspense>`. Dùng skeleton thay vì spinner khi có thể.

```tsx
export default function RoomLoading() {
  return (
    <div className="space-y-4">
      {Array.from({ length: 3 }).map((_, i) => (
        <div key={i} className="h-24 animate-pulse rounded bg-muted" />
      ))}
    </div>
  )
}
```

### Error (`error.tsx`)

Bắt buộc là Client Component.

```tsx
"use client"

export default function RoomError({ error, reset }: { error: Error; reset: () => void }) {
  return (
    <div className="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 p-8">
      <p className="text-destructive">{error.message}</p>
      <button onClick={reset} className="text-sm underline">Thử lại</button>
    </div>
  )
}
```

### Not Found (`not-found.tsx`)

```tsx
import Link from "next/link"

export default function RoomNotFound() {
  return (
    <div className="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 p-8">
      <p className="text-muted-foreground">Không tìm thấy phòng.</p>
      <Link href="/room" className="text-sm underline">Quay lại danh sách</Link>
    </div>
  )
}
```

Trigger bằng cách gọi `notFound()` từ `next/navigation` trong Server Component khi data không tồn tại.

